gmake 4.3 changed the handling of include file open failures
https://hg.openjdk.java.net/jdk/jdk/rev/0743e1d49930

Index: make/common/MakeBase.gmk
--- make/common/MakeBase.gmk.orig
+++ make/common/MakeBase.gmk
